snippet.title: Codemancer Chapter 1 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as Aurora, a girl who must learn more about Magic to rescue her Father -- but beware!  Magic in Aurora's world works the way Computer Programming does in ours.

https://codemancergame.com

Trailer by Affinity Archives: http://www.affinityarchives.com/
